------------------------------------------------
README for cross-compilation:

Quick installation:

Set CC, PATH variables as required.
./configure --host=arm

After creating Makefile,

against:
libtool: link: cannot build libtool library `libcompat.la' from non-libtool objects on this host: malloc.o realloc.o

in Makefile:
use LTLIBOBJS instead of LIBOBJS.

make
make

ignore docs/*pdf error due to texi2dvi tool.
